{
  "doc_id": "20281",
  "text": "Friedelane triterpenes, Friedel-1-en-3-one, Friedelan-1,3, dione 7 -ol, Friedelan-1,3-dione-24-al, Friedelan-1,3-dione-24-oic acid, 24,25-oxidofriedelan-1,3-dione, 7,24-oxidofriedelan-1,3-dione, and 25,26-oxidofriedelan-1,3-dione are isolated from root bark. Mangiferin, Salacinol, kotalanol, Salaprinol, ponkoranol, and leucopelargonidin monomer, its dimer, and tetramer are also reported from roots of Salacia chinensis [CITATION_1] .",
